 	<li>Fachukandi Pass: The Fachukandi Pass is the main highlight of the trek. Trekkers have to cross the pass, which is located at an altitude of 4,000 meters, to reach the other side. The pass offers stunning views of the surrounding peaks and valleys.</li>
 	<li>Trekking Experience: The Fachukandi Pass Trek is a moderate to difficult level trek that is ideal for experienced trekkers. The trek offers an opportunity to experience the beauty of the Himalayas and enjoy the peaceful surroundings.</li>
